This paper proposes a method for FAQ-based question answering using neural networks and feature extraction. The task involves natural language processing and information retrieval, which are common topics in the computer science sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The learning-to-rank algorithm used in the paper also falls under the sub-category of Computational Complexity (cs.CC).
